rows.label: qev200601_MSG0001
rows.name: Oh, hey! Thanks for coming all this way.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0002
rows.name: You're the one who found my keycard, yeah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0003
rows.name: So, um...can I see it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0004
rows.name: Oh, sweet! This is it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0005
rows.name:
Man, I was going to be hosed like a driveway without
this baby.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0006
rows.name:
I suppose we should talk reward, huh? What do you
say I just transfer it to you later, since it's so much?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_JNK0010
rows.name: Argue

rows.label: qev200601_SEL0011
rows.name: Insist on being paid right now.

rows.label: qev200601_JNK0020
rows.name: Remember

rows.label: qev200601_SEL0021
rows.name: Think about a very similar situation from the past.

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0007
rows.name: Wha?! Wait... YOU were the one who...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0008
rows.name:
Oh man, I didn't even NOTICE! I should have spent
more time looking at your face, I guess.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_JNK0030
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev200601_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Yardley if you have met before.

rows.label: qev200601_JNK0040
rows.name: Demand

rows.label: qev200601_SEL0041
rows.name:
Insist that Yardley pay the prior
reward he still owes you.

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0009
rows.name:
Yeeeeah, I think we met in the Outfitters test hangar
over in the industrial district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Does the name Yardley ring a bell? Good ol' Yardley?
Promised a reward and then totally didn't deliver...?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0011
rows.name: ...Hmm.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0012
rows.name: Heh heh. Guess I have some explaining to do, huh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0013
rows.name: Look, I'll tell you everything, but we can't do it here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0014
rows.name:
Meet me at night, on the lowest level beneath the
administrative district's hangars.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0015
rows.name:
I'll pay you what I owe then, including for all the stuff
you just did.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0016
rows.name: Until then.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0017
rows.name: Ah. So you...do remember. Suppose that's unsurprising.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Guess I have some explaining to do, huh?
But we can't talk here. Too many ears or...something.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0019
rows.name:
Meet me at night, on the lowest level beneath the
administrative district's hangars.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev200601_MSG0020
rows.name:
I'll pay you what I owe then, including for all the stuff
you just did.[ST:wait ]
